<title>Schéma de tags recommandé</title><para>Pour un système similaire à l&apos;exemple, structurez les tags comme ceci en commentaire :</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="comment">/*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>SCHÉMA<sp/>DE<sp/>TAGS<sp/>CAN<sp/>(ID<sp/>0x123)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Byte<sp/>0:<sp/>[HB(1)<sp/>|<sp/>SEQ(3)<sp/>|<sp/>CI(2)<sp/>|<sp/>XX(2)]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Byte<sp/>1:<sp/>[AB(7)<sp/>|<sp/>YY(1)]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Byte<sp/>2-3:<sp/>[EDC(4)<sp/>|<sp/>PADDING(12)]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Byte<sp/>4-5:<sp/>[N2OPS(16)]<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>--<sp/>Pression<sp/>N2O<sp/>(Pa)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Byte<sp/>6-7:<sp/>[TLC(12)<sp/>|<sp/>N2ODVS(1)<sp/>|<sp/>N2OIV(1)<sp/>|<sp/>N2OMV(1)<sp/>|<sp/>XX(1)]</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>Total:<sp/>15<sp/>bits<sp/>utilisés,<sp/>reste<sp/>pour<sp/>extension</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*/</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
